北地方法院\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　3 　　月　　23　　日\r\n                              檢　察　官  黃育仁","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1580%2c20220502%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,簡,1580,20220502,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1580","JDATE":"20220502","JTITLE":"竊盜"}